the serpent was a 1916 american silent drama film directed by raoul walsh and starring theda bara . the film based on the short story " the wolf 's claw " , by philip &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; , and its scenario was written by raoul a. walsh . produced and distributed by fox film corporation , the serpent was shot on location at chimney rock , north carolina , and at the fox studio in fort lee , new jersey . it is now considered lost .